	<section id="recipe">
		<p>
			After the success of my last <a
				href="http://www.lilachop.com/article019.html">Chocolate
				Chip Protein Cookie</a> recipe, I decided to
			try making them again. This time, with peanut butter.
			(If you like peanut butter, you're going to love these!)
			Soft, moist peanut butter fudge with chocolate
			chunks, all rolled into a healthy, protein-packed cookie. 
			All it takes is 5 ingredients and a craving for peanut
			butter to make this delicious, <span class="nm">Lila,
				Chop!</span> recipe for beginners.
			<figure>
				<img src="article020crosssectioncookie.jpg" alt="Cross section of cookie" /> 
				<figcaption>Cross-section of a fudgey Peanut Butter protein cookie.</figcaption>
			</figure>
		</p>

